Sentencas: In this paper, are presented our results on the deposition of porous La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-delta (LSFC) based-cathode thick films for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) by a simple and efficient method, the screen-printing technique.
Titulo: POROUS La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-δ - BASED CATHODE MATERIALS FOR INTERMEDIATE TEMPERATURE SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, DEPOSITED BY SCREEN-PRINTING METHOD

Sentencas: LSFC single-phase powder with perovskite structure and rhombohedral symmetry has been obtained by citrate-EDTA method.
Titulo: POROUS La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-δ - BASED CATHODE MATERIALS FOR INTERMEDIATE TEMPERATURE SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, DEPOSITED BY SCREEN-PRINTING METHOD

Sentencas: LSFC and LSFC-based composite (containing 80% LSFC and 20% Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta) powders were screen-printing deposited as layers on Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (CG20) electrolyte ceramic bodies using polyethyleneglycol as binder.
Titulo: POROUS La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-δ - BASED CATHODE MATERIALS FOR INTERMEDIATE TEMPERATURE SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, DEPOSITED BY SCREEN-PRINTING METHOD

Sentencas: LSFC and LSFC-based composite layers were investigated by X-ray diffraction and scanning electron microscopy.
Titulo: POROUS La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-δ - BASED CATHODE MATERIALS FOR INTERMEDIATE TEMPERATURE SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, DEPOSITED BY SCREEN-PRINTING METHOD

Sentencas: The cathode layers sintered at 1200 degrees C, 4h present high porosity, small particles and chemical stability, as well as good adherence on the substrate.
Titulo: POROUS La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3-δ - BASED CATHODE MATERIALS FOR INTERMEDIATE TEMPERATURE SOLID OXIDE FUEL CELLS, DEPOSITED BY SCREEN-PRINTING METHOD
